\section{Population}
\label{sec:personal_action_population}
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%

Personal action for population.

Support things that correlate with fertility rate reduction:

Education for young girls, especially in poor countries.

Economic development in lower HDI countries (tradeoff: increased energy consumption)

Limit family size?

Adoption?

Spatial population distribution. Are people where they want to be?
Urban vs.\ rural, international distribution.
(Connections to land use. 
Is population growth or migration driving this?)
Biggest predictor of happiness is the length of your commute (find source).


