Spend money on low-energy intensity goods and services.

Don't be a billionaire 
(See \url{https://theconversation.com/private-planes-mansions-and-superyachts-what-gives-billionaires-like-musk-and-abramovich-such-a-massive-carbon-footprint-152514}.)  
